<h3 id="addvectors-a-vector2-b-vector2-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#addvectors-a-vector2-b-vector2-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2.addVectors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">addVectors<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( a : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, b : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
