<h3 id="applymatrix3-m-matrix3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#applymatrix3-m-matrix3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2.applyMatrix3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">applyMatrix3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( m : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Matrix3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Matrix3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
