<h3 id="clampscalar-min-float-max-float-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#clampscalar-min-float-max-float-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2.clampScalar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">clampScalar<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( min : Float, max : Float ) : this</h3>
