<h3 id="distancetosquared-v-vector2-float" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#distancetosquared-v-vector2-float" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2.distanceToSquared" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">distanceToSquared<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( v : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : Float</h3>
